text: Antonie Eugenie Yvonne Straeteman (17 July 1907 - 31 January 1998) was a French gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:1998 deaths Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics
